// ================= PART 94 — NATIVE LIVE CLASSROOM FOUNDATION =================
// NAXORA OS 2.0 Native Live Classroom Foundation.
// This part creates the safe foundation for browser-native live classes:
// classroom preview, room policy, device readiness, network readiness, join-token
// preview, participant permissions, chat/hand-raise placeholders and VANI live
// classroom commands. It does not yet implement production WebRTC signalling,
// screen sharing/whiteboard/recording. Those arrive in Parts 95-97.

