// ================= PART 96 — LIVE CHAT, POLLS AND HAND RAISE =================
// NAXORA OS 2.0 Live Chat, Polls and Hand Raise.
// This part adds classroom interaction foundation: moderated live chat, teacher poll
// preview, student vote preview, hand raise queue preview and VANI classroom interaction
// commands. This is socket-ready foundation mode; production realtime WebSocket/WebRTC
// persistence will be connected later. It does not include recording/attendance yet.

